<apex:page contentType="{!if(isDownload,'application/msword#'+docName,'text/HTML')}" applyBodyTag="false" showHeader="false" sidebar="false" standardStylesheets="false" renderAs="{!if(!isDownload,'pdf','')}" standardController="Case" extensions="UpgradeConfirmationController">

    <head>
        <style type="text/css" media="print">
            div.header {
                padding-top: 50px;
                position: running(header);
            }

            @page {
                @top-center {
                    content: element(header);
                }
            
                @bottom-left {
                    content: element(footer);
                }
            }
        </style>    
        
        <style type="text/css">
        @page {
           size: A4;
           margin: 20mm 16mm 20mm 16mm;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Times New Roman Georgia;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding-top: 35px;
        }
        
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border: none;
        }
        
        td,
        th {
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .text-above {
            margin-top: 0px;
        }
        
        .text-below {
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            color: black;
        }
        
        .col {
            float: left;
        }
        
        .clear {
            display: table;
            clear: both;
        }
        
        .gray-box {
            background-color: rgb(185, 185, 185);
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            padding: 5px 10px 5px 10px;
        }
        
        .padded {
            padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px;
        }
        
        label {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 80px;
            height: 34px;
        }
        
        input[type=checkbox] {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            border: 1px solid rgb(180, 6, 170);
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .with-checkbox {
            width: 9%;
            margin-left: 28px;
            margin-top: 7px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: square;
            padding:0;
            margin:0;
        }

        li { 
            padding-left: 1em; 
            text-indent: -.7em;
        }

        .header_download {
            padding-right: 15px;
            position: running(header);
        }

        .list-row {
    background:#f4f4f4;
    display:inline-block;
    border:2px solid red;}

.list-left {
    width:auto;
    padding:10px;
    float:left;
    border: 2px solid blue;}

.list-right {
    padding:10px;
    float:right;
    border:2px solid green;}

        </style>
    </head>
    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="header" rendered="{!!isDownload}">
        <div align="right">{!view.runningNumber}</div>
    </apex:outputPanel>
    <body>
