                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 20px;">
                        <div align="left">
                            <p style="text-indent: 50px; overflow:auto;">
                                This  certificate  entitles  you  to <span style="text-decoration: underline;">a {!view.travelType} confirmed  upgrade</span> to  one  class  higher  from that stated  on  your ticket,  except STA/SATA,  bartered,  redeemed,  award  or  no  fare  tickets, on  Thai Airways  International  operated  flight only.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-left: 50px;padding-right: 20px;">
                        <div align="left">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    This certificate is exclusively used for the passenger whose name appears on the certificate.<br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Upgrade travel must be completed before the expiry date.<br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Mileages will be accrued according to the class of service as indicated in the original ticket.<br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Any other certificates or award tickets may not be applied with this certificate in order  to obtain a double upgrade.<br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Any additional applicable taxes and fee surcharges relevant to the upgrade are under passenger's own responsibility.<br />
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    This certificate cannot be reissued to replace the original one in case of loss, damage or missing.<br />
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 20px;">
                        <div align="left">
                            <p style="text-indent: 50px;">
                                Please  present  this  certificate  to  THAI  staff  at  any  THAI <span style="font-weight: bold;">town  ticketing  offices</span> for reservation  in  advance,  no  later  than  7  working  days  prior  to  the  date  of  travel,  subject  to  seat availability  at the time of making  reservation.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-left: 20px;padding-right: 20px;">
